title: Fake Cubans Shut Down, Four Kicks, and Origins Maduro
itunes:title: Fake Cubans Shut Down, Four Kicks, and Origins Maduro
description: This week's show finds the guys celebrating the arrest of a fake Cuban cartel in Florida. They Smoke Four Kicks and help Jesus Fuego test market his new Origins Maduro. Thanksgiving, Black Friday, and a Smoking ban just in time for the Super Bowl plus a whole lot more....this week on the Cigar Authority!
